### Get All Products - Basic
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - With Search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?search=laptop
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - With Category Filter
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?category_id=1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - With Brand Filter
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?brand_id=1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - With Price Range
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?min_price=1000000&max_price=5000000
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - Sort by Price Ascending
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?sort=price_asc
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - Sort by Price Descending
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?sort=price_desc
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - Sort by Name A-Z
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?sort=name_asc
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - Sort by Name Z-A
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?sort=name_desc
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - Newest First (Default)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?sort=newest
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - Oldest First
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?sort=oldest
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - Featured Products Only
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?featured=true
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - With Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?page=1&limit=12
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - Page 2
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?page=2&limit=12
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - Status Filter
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?status=ACTIVE
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - On Sale Only
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?is_on_sale=true
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - Complex Query
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?search=laptop&category_id=1&min_price=10000000&max_price=30000000&sort=price_asc&page=1&limit=10&featured=true
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get All Products - Combined Filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?brand_id=1&category_id=2&min_price=5000000&status=ACTIVE&sort=newest&page=1&limit=20
Content-Type: application/json
